                               BUBBLE BOBBLE


- Level Select : (Not working with Final Bubble Bobble)

Enter password 3V35NLLE then select 'Continue' Up+Down selects
starting level.

- Cheat mode :

Highlight the "Password" option on the title screen and press Pause.
Press 1, Left, Down, Up, 1, Up, 1, Up. Extra lives and all power-ups
will be available during game play.

- Bonus room :

Begin game play and blow bubbles around the three opponents on level one.
Do not pop the bubbles. Blow bubbles around the opponents after they turn
red. Avoid Baron von Blubba, and keep putting the opponents in bubbles
