@NODE LEMMIN

                                 LEMMINGS


Level select :

Hold 1 + 2 and sweep the D-pad clockwise in a Full-Circle approximately
twenty times at the Sega logo. The sound of a bell will confirm correct
code entry. A level select prompt will appear after a difficulty level
is selected. Press Left or Right to select a new starting level and
press 2 to continue.

