                               S P E C I A L

                        MASTER SYSTEM (v1) HARDWARE


Maze mini-game :

The original Sega Master System model has a built in maze game that can
be accessed through two possible methods, depending on console type.
Hold Up + 1 + 2 at the instruction screen or hold those buttons down and
turn on the game console until the game appears.

