@NODE TEDBOY

                                 TEDDY BOY

THREE ADVANTAGEOUS SELECTIONS:
While in the Title Screen, move the Directional Pad UP, DOWN,
LEFT, and RIGHT.  A new screen will appear with your three
options,  "Continue", "Fire", and "1-P".

CONTINUE:  Lets you continue from the last round you finished.
To continue, choose "yes".  You can't do this at the beginning of
the game, you have to have played and passed round 1!

FIRE:  Makes it so Teddy Boy's floor will not disappear under
him.  To choose this option, choose "No".

1-P:   Makes the game play in a one or two player mode.  To get
the two-player mode, choose "No".

ROUND SELECTION:  While in the previously mentioned screen, move
the Directional Pad UP once, then DOWN nine times, and press
BUTTON #1.  On the bottom of the screen, "Round" will appear,
followed by a number.  By pushing the Control Pad to the LEFT and
RIGHT, you will choose your rounds from 1-50.  When done, press
BUTTON #1 to start at the level you have selected.

@ENDNODE
