Miscellaenous Hints:
To find the Shrine of Spirituality, go to the right of the City
of Minoc.  There will be a Moongate that will appear, when the
moons are Full.  If you have the Rune of Spirituality, just enter
the Moongate, when the moons are full.

A player can't have two of the same profession in his party.

The number of characters you can have in your party is determined
by the level of your character, EG: Level 5, four people can
join, Level 2, only one person can.

