                         SEGA MASTER SYSTEM CHEATS

                                Version1.10




Version         History
==============  =======================================================

1.00            First release.  Only appeared on Amiga Format cover CD.
                It is based on Jeff Bogumil Master System Cheats Col-
                lection wich was a simple ascii text format.
                @{" Read original note by Jeff " LINK JEFF }

1.01            Nothing added/changed, first public release to Aminet.

1.10            80 games added and 17 updated, this makes a total of
                171 games covered.  Most updates are coming from the
                www.gamewinners.com homepage wich covers a large united
                list of cheats for many consoles/computers.

                Also made shorter lists of names, previously A-M, N-Z
                changed to A-H, I-P & Q-Z mostly for ease of use.

                Still passwords to add for Populus and Tennis Ace but
                I'm a bit bored of typing...  I'll do it later.


Hope you enjoy those cheats and if you find newer version(s) of these
cheats (or others) send them to me, I will update this file. Please
prefer CHEATS, if you want to include solutions, type'em yourself
(maximum 74 chars wide) and send'em attached to your mail (ZIP or LHA).

You can always contact me by e-mail : - hibisch@be.tf
                                      - hibisch@yahoo.com

Also visit my homepage (C64 archives waiting for download) at :

                             www.hibisch.be.tf

